    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p><strong>Sami Faisal</strong>, founder of <strong>Rank Hub</strong>, just 15 — based in Faisalabad, Pakistan. Proud Muslim. Self-taught hustler. Turning online skills into income.</p>
    <p>Started early, learned fast. Balancing school & freelancing. Working with global clients. Building a digital brand with pro-level skills.</p>

    <h2>About This Site</h2>
    <p><strong>Rank Hub</strong> is more than a service site — it’s your digital partner. No fake promises. No fluff. Just real, result-driven work.</p>
    <p>From guest posting to tool reselling, design, editing, SEO, and daily services — this is what I live and breathe.</p>

    <h2>My Core Skills</h2>
    <p>Services include <strong>Guest Posting, Content Writing, Tool Reselling, Editing, Design</strong>, and more. Real skills. Real clients. Real results.</p>
    <p>Resell tools like Ahrefs, Canva Pro, Grammarly, ChatGPT Plus — fast and supported. Editing includes PDFs, Word, resumes, images. Design includes logos, thumbnails, posters, branding kits.</p>
    <p>Also offer basic website dev using HTML/CSS, dark themes, SEO, and clean UI. I handle on-page SEO, metadata, and keyword research.</p>

    <h2>Why Work With Me</h2>
    <p>Because I care. I reply fast, deliver clean, no excuses. Clear, consistent, and communication-first work.</p>
